body_html:
ClientEnvironment.jsm#L109

if (mostRecentPings[ping.type].timeStampCreated < ping.timeStampCreated)
should be:
if (mostRecentPings[ping.type].timestampCreated < ping.timestampCreated)

(ie. timeStampCreated should be timestampCreated)
title: Typo in recipe-client-addon telemetry test
body:
[ClientEnvironment.jsm#L109](https://github.com/mozilla/normandy/blob/master/recipe-client-addon/lib/ClientEnvironment.jsm#L109)

`if (mostRecentPings[ping.type].timeStampCreated < ping.timeStampCreated)`
should be:
`if (mostRecentPings[ping.type].timestampCreated < ping.timestampCreated)`

(ie. `timeStampCreated` should be `timestampCreated`)
